thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by McFarlane family

author: McFarlane family
title: McFarlane family
text: We rented a car for a portion of a trip to New Zealand. The service when we picked up the car was great, the car worked well for us (tho' we wished it had a USB or AUX port so that we could've played our own music when we couldn't catch a NZ radio station), and turning the car in at the end went very smoothly. The gentleman at the drop-off site even gave us a ride to the ferry, which we appreciated!
